arty. July 9, 2020 In "News" Deceit was undoubtedly the setting for a reconciliatory meeting between the Peoples Democratic Party, PDP national chairman, Alhaji Bamanga Tukur and the members of the party National Working Committee, NWC last Wednesday. January 25, 2013 In "Politics"